<BaseLayout title="About | Very Cool Person" description="About verycoolperson.com">
	<section class="page-header">
		<p class="eyebrow">About</p>
		<h1>About me</h1>
		<p class="lede">A short introduction goes here.</p>
	</section>

	<section class="prose">
		<p>
			Use this page for the human version of your bio: what you care about, what you are working on,
			and what people should know before following your work.
		</p>
		<p>
			You can keep this warm and personal, while the <a href="/cv">CV</a> page can stay structured and
			professional.
		</p>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
